{"tid":2426382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實乜野叫\"賺藍店錢 有乜問題\"?","createTime":"2021-02-28T05:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T06:20:36.000Z","uid":98473,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"54d3b250be93ee821b365e259b43b8ecf440a84d","tid":2426382,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"我好多朋友都係響藍店返工<br />\n但成日講到自己賺藍店錢 有乜問題<br />\n講到自己好似好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藍店蝕撚晒錢咁<br />\n大佬 人地藍店比10蚊你做野 你就幫返藍店賺1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姜濤幫藍店賣廣告 賺藍店錢 有乜問題<br />\n人地賣一賣廣告 大撚把人因為姜濤去食M記<br />\n人地M記賺撚到FATFAT<br />\n你地就話賺藍店錢 有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都一樣係藍店返工 但我真係講唔出咁撚ON9既&quot;賺藍店錢 有乜問題&quot;理由<br />\n我係為搵食姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed20c58174faa010547056cabc1ed5a0a8785aa","tid":2426382,"uid":134087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"秒經"},{"pid":"da5887bb567f64fd09b05d04bdc920fd9ee37907","tid":2426382,"uid":252784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"哦 咁賺藍店錢有咩問題<br />\n支持姜B掠麥當勞水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e6dca1fe370866586b802969f388fa72b00f7b","tid":2426382,"uid":306337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"其實警察都係賺政府錢姐 有咩所謂喎"},{"pid":"deaf5843b23f66e0e610c8ac901a0916fadc581e","tid":2426382,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"賺藍錢入黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af28d0b7da43581a5bd7ece1dad3c54f6b0ee562","tid":2426382,"uid":253016,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"唔關事<br />\n藍店賺唔賺錢去關有冇客去<b